## Trust OS v0.1 Completion Statement

Trust OS v0.1 is now structurally complete as an experimental trust layer between Gratitude OS and Royalty OS.

This version defines the core documents, JSON Schemas, YAML examples, and validation workflow required to represent how gratitude marks can be transformed into trust events and accumulated into trust profiles.

Trust OS v0.1 does not define money, legal rights, or automatic royalty entitlement.

It defines a non-monetary trust layer:

```text
Existence Proof → Gratitude → Trust → Royalty

With GitHub Actions validation passing, Trust OS v0.1 has moved from concept to machine-verifiable specification.

This is the first working foundation for converting recognition into accumulated trust.
